entries.femaleVariant: I'm a member of the Greyer family. I'd like to see the body.
I'm afraid that won't be possible. Access to the morgue is employee-restricted.
How's it goin'? Hey, you got special offers?
Depends. You want to cremate somebody? Or make a purchase for yourself?
Don't you think it's a little too soon for me?
Always better to be insured. If you pay now, you can get a fifty percent discount with our latest "Cremation-Salvation" package.
Come on now, that's just too good to be true.
But it is true! The details are in our complimentary information booklet.
